schools.name: Rim Of The World Senior High School

data.description: Welcome home to your new 3 bedroom, 3 bath home on the mountain! The main level has two bedrooms, and two baths while the lower level of the home features an additional studio apartment/in-law suite complete with its own separate entrance! Live upstairs while you rent out the bottom or bring your parents/in-laws (also great for older kids)! Other features include a GARAGE, a level fenced-in BACKYARD, a LOFT, front DECK, and back PATIO area! Don't wait, come tour soon!
